overview.en: Youdeal is a blockchain enabled marketplace platform for personal services industry based on an ecosystem with 50 million users globally.  In Youdeal alliance, there are 6 million individual service providers, exceeding 100 million transactions so far, achieving more than 60 billion RMB turnover, and 400 cities in coverage. Personal service industry that Youdeal is tackling has a market size in trillions. It is predicted that there will be 40% people being freelancer in the future. The consumers demand will greatly promote the growth of users and market scale.
overview.zh: YouDeal是基于区块链的全球化个人自由交易平台。YouDeal与全球最大的个人服务交易生态结盟，YouDeal联盟生态累计5000万的用户、600万的服务达人、累计撮合订单1亿单、累计撮合金额报价600亿人民币，行业兴趣覆盖健身、游戏、电影、等上百种。去公司、去老板、去房租的去中心化模式可以提高个人劳动资源的配置、释放出更多的个人经济价值。
